From: AIC8800 Firmware Fix <fix@aic8800.local>
Date: Thu, 19 Jun 2026 16:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] 修复 AIC8800D80 芯片固件路径问题

此补丁修复了 AIC8800D80 芯片在加载固件时的路径构造问题。

原始代码只处理了 AIC8800DC 和 AIC8800D80N 芯片的固件路径，
缺少对 AIC8800D80 芯片的处理，导致固件文件无法正确加载。

修复内容:
- 在 aic_load_firmware 函数中添加 PRODUCT_ID_AIC8800D80 的判断
- AIC8800D80 芯片使用默认路径（不带子目录），与其他芯片不同

测试结果:
- 蓝牙补丁表 fw_patch_table_8800d80_u02.bin 正常加载
- Wi-Fi 固件正常加载
- 蓝牙设备 hci0 成功创建并可扫描周围设备

Signed-off-by: AIC8800 Firmware Fix <fix@aic8800.local>
---
 src/USB/driver_fw/drivers/aic_btusb/aic_btusb.c | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

--- a/src/USB/driver_fw/drivers/aic_btusb/aic_btusb.c	2026-06-19 15:59:24.920463734 +0800
+++ b/src/USB/driver_fw/drivers/aic_btusb/aic_btusb.c	2026-06-19 16:01:49.400554514 +0800
@@ -3068,6 +3068,9 @@
             len = snprintf(path, FW_PATH_MAX, "%s/%s/%s",aic_default_fw_path, "aic8800DC", name);
         } else if (g_chipid == PRODUCT_ID_AIC8800D80N) {
             len = snprintf(path, FW_PATH_MAX, "%s/%s/%s",aic_default_fw_path, "aic8800D80N", name);
+        } else if (g_chipid == PRODUCT_ID_AIC8800D80) {
+            // Use default path without subdirectory for AIC8800D80
+            len = snprintf(path, FW_PATH_MAX, "%s/%s",aic_default_fw_path, name);
         } else {
             printk("%s unknown chipid %d\n", __func__, g_chipid);
         }
